name: Licensure by endorsement
text: [§451K-8]  Licensure by endorsement.  The director shall grant, upon application and payment of proper fees, licensure to an individual who, at the time of application, holds a valid license as a genetic counselor issued by another state, territory, or jurisdiction if the requirements for that certification or license are equal to, or greater than, the requirements of this chapter. [L 2009, c 191, pt of §2]
